rating specific metadata for `libcore.io.Memory`. But then, thereâ€™s this user-code-filter I need to check. Iâ€™ll have to clarify how that filter interacts with method registration.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_OTFHFHw7U7QQsjRni7jQYuFo|fc_06c798cc4e0b3edc0169f73c04511081968729f4ff26b2d9a7", "name": "read", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/org.apache.pekko/pekko-protobuf-v3_3/1.0.1/user-code-filter.json"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1854, "output": 830, "cacheRead": 54784, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 57468, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777810423281, "responseId": "resp_06c798cc4e0b3edc0169f73bf7d8548196a75cd4b444e10b94"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_OTFHFHw7U7QQsjRni7jQYuFo|fc_06c798cc4e0b3edc0169f73c04511081968729f4ff26b2d9a7", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"rules\": [\n    {\n      \"excludeClasses\": \"**\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"includeClasses\": \"org.apache.pekko.protobufv3.internal.**\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777810436746}]}
